{"tid":686741,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"15歲道枝駿佑鹿眼「比女孩美」爆紅　被封為「千年難得一見美少男」","createTime":"2018-06-01T14:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T16:51:33.000Z","uid":9573,"like":9,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a14d3c59acc5488c9be72dab24b589564c6edeb1","tid":686741,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/448/d448875.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F448%2Fd448875.jpg&h=6b06f615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲橋本環奈因這張照片被封為「千年難得一見美少女」。<br />\n<br />\n日本女星橋本環奈因一張「奇蹟美照」打開知名度，被封為「千年難得一見美少女」，現在也有一名日本男星，因清新氣質和亮眼外型，被封為「千年難得一見美少男」、「千年一遇美少男」，粉絲為其製作的表情包在各社群平台上瘋傳，他就是年僅15歲的道枝駿佑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3321/d3321766.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3321%2Fd3321766.jpg&h=6d7a8289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲▼道枝駿佑清秀外型擄獲眾多少女和姊姊的心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3321/d3321764.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3321%2Fd3321764.jpg&h=2f5f85f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3321/d3321816.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3321%2Fd3321816.jpg&h=f810b4cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.hoopchina.com.cn/uploads/star/event/images/151026/032b6fe1131a0eaa59b97df4150745e781191e84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.hoopchina.com.cn%2Fuploads%2Fstar%2Fevent%2Fimages%2F151026%2F032b6fe1131a0eaa59b97df4150745e781191e84.jpg&h=87066b04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲道枝駿佑演出《成為母親》後備受矚目。<br />\n<br />\n道枝駿佑生於2002年，12歲時看到電視劇《金田一少年之事件簿》，非常崇拜山田涼介，因此向傑尼斯遞出了申請書，並成功入社成為練習生，2017年演出首部連續劇《成為母親》，飾演澤尻英龍華及藤木直人的兒子，年僅14歲就有自然率真的演技，加上清秀亮麗的外型，吸引不少少女粉絲的心，因而有「千年難得一見美少男」的稱號，也被視為演藝圈未來的一顆明亮新星。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3321/d3321765.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3321%2Fd3321765.jpg&h=e3f5856a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲道枝駿佑被視為是明日之星。"},{"pid":"52447beeb00c79b5528d9bf86063ae2816b89d0d","tid":686741,"uid":174115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:29:48.000Z","msg":"Gay test fail"},{"pid":"2c19e0817850edf8a15cf13e02b1d0ebdb60eeed","tid":686741,"uid":12755,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:30:26.000Z","msg":"阿蘇亂入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fec5fae3c597746fd2d0d22d85f396a6646b588","tid":686741,"uid":29649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:31:24.000Z","msg":"正過橋本<br />\n<br />\n非基"},{"pid":"3e0ec615772a8ca69287f2346c8b0e20a3c12fe5","tid":686741,"uid":137725,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:31:28.000Z","msg":"張相post錯左個南亞裔人............................"},{"pid":"2f6fa39d3a49af59a557b44d14d56e1a8c807dc8","tid":686741,"uid":1712,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:32:39.000Z","msg":"朱千雪呢？"},{"pid":"e42e37ab04b5b7b6ea2b1e1187b64b0a3e57f497","tid":686741,"uid":5384,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:34:49.000Z","msg":"嘩<br />\n真係「比女孩美」喎<br />\n都係留返畀識食之人"},{"pid":"cd9d4087a295f8f5d3a657c1eddcbda1cc652388","tid":686741,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:41:11.000Z","msg":"後入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7287cb3ef68dd32c0174a725dd81338cb1c6c2e2","tid":686741,"uid":27247,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:45:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/224455_a27e390ad1a3220ff96344e17e918d96.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/